{"tid":1405614,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［推比前線睇］快棄寶林站！！","createTime":"2019-08-04T10:32:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-04T12:27:03.000Z","uid":115977,"like":104,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"0cff7bbf279f65877d43d3a3dc8c19d85aadda97","tid":1405614,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:32:28.000Z","msg":"一係你地就係狗衝出黎既時候，即刻轉場或者散水！<br />\n<br />\n如果唔係，真係<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>唔好守寶林站！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n狗屋就係新都城二期後面<br />\n佢地連車都唔撚使坐就已經到寶林站<br />\n<br />\n1.啲狗行地面<br />\n佢行馬路或者巴士站穿過黎就已經到寶林站門口<br />\n你地擺路障係馬路完全係無撚用<br />\n除非你擺埋路障係行人路<br />\n<br />\n2. 啲狗行天橋<br />\n欣明苑條天橋連撚住新都城二期<br />\n佢地可以入二期再落地鐵條電梯<br />\n就完全可以block撚哂地鐵站所有入閘機<br />\n<br />\n你地守係個度完全係同守緊一個死角無分別！<br />\n<br />\n5:00pm 翠林有一架狗車<br />\n<br />\n6:30pm 有好多狗車經康盛落去寶林<br />\n（factchecked )<br />\n<br />\n利申：翠林撚"},{"pid":"1308750a51e06caeed6cfa0a3427d100f23d38e7","tid":1405614,"uid":87041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:39:09.000Z","msg":"推~~"},{"pid":"68934f004f46e464e69f3c881dffa9a900be0d02","tid":1405614,"uid":98431,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:41:50.000Z","msg":"85大局為重<br />\n<br />\n勿轉場勿磨爛蓆"},{"pid":"5db1ad73bd673117c0ad91ec845a19dd3c36a048","tid":1405614,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:42:59.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c861226df8f204f2f06122ab1faf8615cb86ccd6","tid":1405614,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:43:19.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"17af5b0b0eea50c6908550fcd83888b294dc74d5","tid":1405614,"uid":115977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:43:27.000Z","msg":"留命！<br />\n有咩留返罷完工之後先繼續玩！"},{"pid":"af9a7179d25ddadabc12c0884bb504b871350cbb","tid":1405614,"uid":259515,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-04T10:43:30.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"2602ae